Package: graphsim
Type: Package
Title: Simulate Expression data from iGraph networks 
Version: 0.1.0
Date: 2019-02-05
Authors@R: c(person("S. Thomas", "Kelly",email = "tom.kelly@postgrad.otago.ac.nz", role = c("ctb")),
             person("S. Thomas", "Kelly",email = "tom.kelly@riken.jp", role = c("aut", "cre")),
             person("Michael A.", "Black", email = "mik.black@otago.ac.nz", role = c("aut", "ths")))
Description: Functions to develop simulated continuous data (e.g., gene expression) from a sigma covariance matrix derived from a graph structure in iGraph. Intended to extend mvtnorm to take iGraph structures rather than sigma matrices as input.
License: GPL-3
Imports:
